-   <span data-ttu-id="c4c44-117"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A> 属性为 `null`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4c44-117">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A> property is `null`.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="c4c44-118">) 返回的人工语义置信度为 1.0 (<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4c44-118">An artificial semantic confidence level of 1.0 (returned by <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A>).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c4c44-119">通常，应用程序会 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> 间接创建实例， <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> 并使用和实例将它们添加到对象，以及 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey>  <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 和和 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4c44-119">Typically, applications create <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> instances indirectly, adding them to <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> objects by using <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey> instances,  in conjunction with  <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> objects.</span></span>  
  
